snippet.title: Among Trees - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A small vibrant survival sandbox adventure, Among Trees is set in a colorful wilderness world teeming with life. Heading to Steam Early Access in 2019.
Add Among Trees to your wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/897730/Among_Trees/

Among Trees has been in development for 1,5 years.

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/amongtreesgame/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/amongtreesgame
Web: https://www.amongtreesgame.com/
